snippet.title: Overcooked 2 - Free Chinese New Year Update | PS4
snippet.description: As the Onion Kingdom sizzles with celebration for Chinese New Year, the Onion King would like to wish all you valiant chefs a year filled with joy, prosperity and plentiful platefuls. And what better way to celebrate than by grabbing your nearest and dearest and preparing to chop, cook, serve (and maybe shout) your way through seven succulent new levels!
